analysis.title: Global Market Outlook
analysis.content: A GMS score of 38 maintains a Defensive regime, though upward momentum pushed the score from 34, signaling a stabilizing sentiment floor. While DXY (Dollar strength/Liquidity) and VIX (Fear/Volatility) remain elevated, tightening credit spreads provide a crucial tailwind for recovery. Investors must watch geopolitical friction in semiconductors; Taiwan's relocation pushback could create a structural ceiling for tech gains. Maintain a risk-off posture with selective entries until the index reclaims the 40 level.

reports.ID: Skor GMS 38 mempertahankan rezim Defensif, meskipun momentum kenaikan mendorong skor dari 34, menandakan stabilisasi sentimen pasar. Sementara DXY (Kekuatan Dolar/Likuiditas) dan VIX (Ketakutan/Volatilitas) tetap tinggi, penyempitan spread kredit memberikan dorongan bagi pemulihan. Waspadai gesekan geopolitik pada sektor semikonduktor; penolakan relokasi oleh Taiwan dapat membatasi reli saham teknologi. Tetap pertahankan posisi waspada dan selektif dalam memilih aset hingga indeks kembali melampaui level ambang batas 40.
